== Yoland Makolo ==
kuwa 30 Nyakanga 2021nibwo ibiro bya [[Ministry of Infrastructure (Rwanda) - MININFRA|Minisitiri]] wintebe byatangaje k Yoland Makolo

yagizwe umuvugizi wa [[Geworugiya|Guverinoma]] muri minisiteri yububanyi namahanga nubutwererane<ref>https://www.kigalitoday.com/amakuru/amakuru-mu-rwanda/article/yolande-makolo-yagizwe-umuvugizi-wa-guverinoma-muri-minisiteri-y-ububanyi-n-amahanga</ref>

== Amateka ==
Yoland Makolo yavukiye muri [[kongo]] papa we umubyara akaba ari umu kongoman wo mubwoko

bwa Luba mugace bita [[Congo Brazzaville|Kassai]] na Nyina wu umunyarwandakazi<ref>https://www.kapitalafrik.com/2021/08/02/rwanda-yolande-makolo-appointed-government-spokesperson/</ref>

== Agashya ==
Yoland Makolo ni umuvandimwe wa [[Yvonne Makolo]] uyoboye ikigo gikomeye

mu Rwanda kizwi nka [[Rwanda Tribune|Rwandair]]

Yolande Makolo kandi ni inshuti cyane yahafi na nyakubahwa Madamu Jeannette Kagame<ref>https://www.financialafrik.com/2021/08/01/rwanda-yolande-makolo-nommee-porte-parole-du-gouvernement/</ref>

umufasha wa Perezida wu [[Rwanda Tribune|Rwanda]]

== Mbereyaho ==
Yolande makolo yari asanzwe akora mubiro byu Umukuru w'Igihugu yari

ashinzwe gukurikirana ibyerekeranye n' itangazamakuru ndetse n'itumanaho<ref>https://www.kigalitoday.com/amakuru/amakuru-mu-rwanda/article/yolande-makolo-yagizwe-umuvugizi-wa-guverinoma-muri-minisiteri-y-ububanyi-n-amahanga</ref>

